{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 647138, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 133870, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "话是这样，但是现实不是。", "timestamp": 1606895091, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 647144, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 133870, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这里有一个偷换概念，现实是这样的，但不代表现实应该是这样。从来如此，便对吗？", "timestamp": 1606895164, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 647146, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 133870, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 现实是现实，但很多人说什么凭什么比人家三代的时候可不是开玩笑，是真的觉得“你脑子秀逗了人家世袭很正常很合理你命不好哔哔个什么”", "timestamp": 1606895243, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 647163, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 133870, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "现代社会的主流价值观是建立在私有制基础上，而财富积累带来的经济地位不平等是私有制必将导致的结果", "timestamp": 1606895440, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 647170, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 133870, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "所以从马主义出发来看是不合理的，但是大部分人已经习惯了从消费主义视角出发看问题", "timestamp": 1606895517, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 647175, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 133870, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "从你用使用货币的那一刻起，资本主义就已经在你心里扎根了", "timestamp": 1606895551, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 647178, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 133870, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "遗产税？", "timestamp": 1606895594, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 647220, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 133870, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "主要还是知识不能遗传...", "timestamp": 1606896037, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 647296, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 133870, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "保守主义好！保